products.title: MSI Gaming GeForce GTX 1660 192-Bit HDMI/DP 6GB GDRR5 HDCP Support DirectX 12 Dual Fan VR Ready OC Graphics Card (GTX 1660 VENTUS XS 6G OC)
features: Video Memory - 6GB GDDR5. Power consumption- 120 W. Recommended PSU - 450 W
products.description: A fresh new dual fan design, VENTUS proudly displays its industrial shapes in neutral colors to fit any build. Using two of the award-winning to RX fans 2.0, MSI Venture graphics cards provide years of top-notch cooling performance. A sturdy backplate helps to strengthen the graphics card and complements the design to look even better.
